repositories.description:
The Metamodel Zoos are a collaborative open source research effort intended to produce experimental material that may be used by all in the domain of Model Driven Engineering.
This Repository uses the eCore version located at: http://www.emn.fr/z-info/atlanmod/index.php/Ecore.
repositories.name: AtlanZooEcore
